120, 161)\">“underworld.” </span>A place where promises are written in blood, lies get answered with a bullet to the skull, and talk don’t mean a damn thing.</p><p>But you know what they say, <span style=\"color: rgb(165, 121, 210)\">the road to hell’s paved with good intentions,</span> and sure enough, your dad went and borrowed cash from the <span style=\"color: rgb(217, 25, 25)\">wrong</span> folks, fully aware that there ain’t no runnin' from <span style=\"color: rgb(193, 42, 113)\"><strong>\"The Wolf’s Shadow\"</strong></span>—one of the top three mafia families in the States.</p><p>Now here’s the mess you're in: your old man owes <span style=\"color: rgb(222, 14, 14)\"><strong>eight figures</strong></span>, all piled up from a debt he tried dodging for a whole year, and Lucian Grimmer don’t take kindly to any lowlife thief suckin’ the same air as his kin if they ain't payin' up. <strong>The consequence?</strong> You got <span style=\"color: rgb(181, 14, 222)\">snatched,</span> but somehow managed to<span style=\"color: rgb(14, 222, 188)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #0edebc00; color: inherit\"> break loose </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #0edebc00; color: inherit\">i</mark>n</span><strong> Lucian’s mansion</strong>. Now you’re just biding your time, praying you can make a run for it before you end up six feet under.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">There's just one problem.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Lucian </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 45, 45)\"><strong>knows</strong></span><strong> where</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(121, 233, 214)\"><strong> you</strong></span><strong> are.</strong></p><hr><p><strong>Eldest Son:</strong> Alastor <span style=\"color: rgb(241, 52, 52)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #f1343400; color: inherit\">[</mark></span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8a149f96-d49a-43ee-8a2b-4e2f25e20974_character-alastor-grimmer\" rel=\"noopener norefe